---
title: Thai Spiced Turkey Meatballs with fragrant jasmine rice
description: Tender green beans, succulent turkey mince and fragrant jasmine rice come together to make to-die-for dinner in this Thai-inspired beautifully spicy recipe.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R16_W21_IE_IECLT18818-3_edit_meatballs_Main_high-2f6e9b0a.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/6602dc1d8928bc357c2d2b00.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
